
=============================================================================== 
                               Changes in 2.4 (Jul-2016)
===============================================================================

  - Paranoid mode added (adcastel@uji.es)

=============================================================================== 
                               Changes in 2.0 (Jul-2016)
===============================================================================

  - Pthreads API implemented over GLT (adcastel@uji.es)

=============================================================================== 
                               Changes in 1.2 (Jun-2016)
===============================================================================

  - Added TLS module support for Qthreads library to complete Pthreads API and  
    moved to the CORE part(adcastel@uji.es)

=============================================================================== 
                               Changes in 1.1 (Jun-2016)
===============================================================================

  - Now, work units are created directly into an ES when Argobots is used 
    instead of extracting the needed pool (Internally the mechanism is equal) 
    (adcastel@uji.es)

=============================================================================== 
                               Changes in 1.0 (May-2016)
===============================================================================

  - INTERFACE CHANGES: All work unit creation functions follow the pattern:
    glt_ult/tasklet_create*() instead of glt_ult/tasklet_creation*() 
    (adcastel@uji.es)

=============================================================================== 
                               Changes in 0.7 (May-2016)
===============================================================================

  - GLT implemented over Pthreads (adcastel@uji.es)

=============================================================================== 
                               Changes in 0.6 (Apr-2016)
===============================================================================

  - EXTENDED part implemented over MassiveThreads (adcastel@uji.es)

=============================================================================== 
                               Changes in 0.5 (Mar-2016)
===============================================================================

  - EXTENDED part implemented over Qthreads (adcastel@uji.es)

=============================================================================== 
                               Changes in 0.4 (Mar-2016)
===============================================================================

  - EXTENDED part implemented over Argobots (adcastel@uji.es)

